  <brief_title>Efficacy and Safety of TAC and Exemestane as Neoadjuvant Chemotherapy in the Postmenopausal Women With Breast Cancer</brief_title>
  <official_title>Study to Assessment the Efficacy and Safety of Joint TAC and Exemestane as Neoadjuvant Chemotherapy in the Postmenopausal Women With Operable Breast Cancer</official_title>
